<Layout 
  title="Social Parties & Event Catering Ann Arbor | Chef Nam Catering"
  description="Celebrate life's special moments with professional event catering in Ann Arbor, Michigan. Birthday parties, anniversaries, graduations, and social gatherings made memorable."
>
